                     <rs type="person" ref="#pmb2121">Schnitzler</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><rs type="person" ref="#pmb2147">Altenberg</rs> in der
                  Psychiatrie der <rs ref="#pmb153" type="place">Landesheilanstalt Am Steinhof</rs></note>! Ihr<space unit="chars" quantity="3"/><signed>P. A.</signed></p></div>
